# Web-export generation configuration.
#
# One combination per line:
#     <testCases>  <network>  <propagations>  # comment shown on the web page
#
#   <testCases>     base name of a TestCases file  (Resources/InitialData/TestCases/<name>.TestCases.XML)
#   <network>       base name of a Network file    (Resources/InitialData/Networks/<name>.Network.txt)
#   <propagations>  how many propagation steps to record (the trace gets propagations+1 snapshots)
#   # comment       free text after the first '#'; displayed for that network on the web page
#
# A line whose first non-blank character is '#', or a blank line, is ignored.
# Extend this file by adding more lines; re-run tools/generate-web.ps1 afterwards.

and   and     2  # Logical AND
mul3  mul_uni 20 # Multiplication. Multiplies in0 by in1. It needs in0 propagations to calculate the result.  